OL,6,FA Liberal Democrat councillor has
OL,7,Fresigned from a council in
OL,8,FGloucestershire after being convicted
OL,9,Fof sexually assaulting a young girl.
OL,11,FTewkesbury Borough Councillor Paul
OL,12,FOckelton, 60, has been found guilty of
OL,13,Fsexually assaulting a child under 13
OL,14,Fby touching.
OL,16,FGloucester Crown Court heard how the
OL,17,F60-year-old sat his victim on his lap
OL,18,Fand asked her "Do you like this?"
OL,19,Fwhile carrying out the assault in
OL,20,FNovember 2021.
