OL,6,FThe girl, who was under 13 at the
OL,7,Ftime, disclosed later that evening
OL,8,Fthat Ockelton had sexually assaulted
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,FOckelton, of Innsworth, told police he
OL,12,Fhad been "brushing her hair" and
OL,13,F"tickling her tummy" but a jury found
OL,14,Fhim guilty of one count of sexual
OL,15,Fassault by touching.
OL,17,FHe was convicted following a four-day
OL,18,Ftrial at Gloucester Crown Court. He
OL,19,Fhas now been bailed and is due to be
OL,20,Fsentenced on 14 April.
