OL,6,FTewkesbury Borough Council's Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat leader Richard Stanley said
OL,8,Fit was a "shocking and disturbing
OL,9,Fcase" and the authority's thoughts are
OL,10,Fwith the victim.
OL,12,F"To be clear, Mr Ockelton withheld the
OL,13,Ffact that there were ongoing
OL,14,Fproceedings during his application
OL,15,Fprocess to stand as a councillor," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
