OL,6,F"As soon as I became aware that he was
OL,7,Fsubject to a criminal court case, I
OL,8,Ftook the steps that I was legally able
OL,9,Fto take, including urging him to
OL,10,Fresign as a councillor, which he
OL,11,Frefused.
OL,13,F"I therefore suspended him from our
OL,14,Fpolitical group so that he could be
OL,15,Fremoved from all committees but wasn't
OL,16,Ffree to take on roles as an
OL,17,Findependent councillor.
