OL,4,C13, while she sat on his lap
OL,6,F"On that basis, we were legally
OL,7,Frestricted in the action that could be
OL,8,Ftaken while court proceedings were
OL,9,Fongoing. However, the council took all
OL,10,Fsteps it could to minimise any risk
OL,11,Fwithout causing prejudice.
OL,13,F"Safeguarding is of paramount
OL,14,Fimportance to the council, and we
OL,15,Fencourage anyone affected by such
OL,16,Fcrimes to access help that is
OL,17,Favailable."
OL,19,FDue to the resignation a vacancy has
OL,20,Farisen for the Innsworth ward and an
OL,21,Felection will be held on 1 May.
